R(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Despite its popularity, The Big Reel struggled financially in the 1990s and eventually ceased publication in 2001.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The Big Reel holds a significant place in the history of film journalism and is remembered as one of the most significant film magazines of its time. Its in-depth coverage of classic Hollywood films and exclusive interviews with industry professionals helped shape the perception of American cinema.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Today, The Big Reel remains a valuable resource for film historians and enthusiasts alike and serves as a testament to the enduring popularity of classic Hollywood films.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

