VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A bi-monthly golf magazine covering travel, lifestyle, and courses around the world, published from 2003 to 2009.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Travel + Leisure Golf was a bi-monthly magazine that focused on the sport and culture of golf. The magazine was first published in 2003, and was the golfing spin-off of Travel + Leisure magazine.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## History' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Travel + Leisure Golf was first published in 2003 in New York, United States. The magazine was founded by American Express Publishing, a subsidiary of American Express Company. The magazine was created as a companion publication to Travel + Leisure magazine, which also focused on travel related topics.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, Travel + Leisure Golf became known for its comprehensive coverage of the golfing world, including news, features, and product reviews.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Content' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Travel + Leisure Golf covered a wide range of topics related to golf, including travel, lifestyle, and golf courses around the world. The magazine also featured profiles of famous golfers and interviews with golf professionals, as well as tips and techniques for improving one''s golf game.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'One of the magazine''s most popular features was its coverage of some of the top golfing events, such as the U.S. Open and British Open. The magazine also included advice for golfers on how to plan golf-themed vacations, and covered some of the most scenic and challenging golf courses in the world.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Impact' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Travel + Leisure Golf played an important role in the golfing community, providing golf enthusiasts with a comprehensive resource for news, information, and reviews of golf-related products and experiences.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine also helped to promote the sport of golf to a wider audience and raised awareness of some of the top golfing destinations and courses around the world.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Cessation of publication' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In 2009, Travel + Leisure Golf stopped publication due to declining advertising revenue caused by the financial crisis that hit the United States. The magazine''s content was merged into Travel + Leisure and Golf Digest.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Conclusion' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Travel + Leisure Golf was a bi-monthly magazine that focused on the sport and culture of golf. The magazine was known for its comprehensive coverage of the golfing world, including news, features, and product reviews. The magazine played an important role in promoting the sport of golf and raising awareness of some of the top golfing destinations and courses around the world. In 2009, the magazine stopped publication due to declining advertising revenue caused by the financial crisis that hit the United States and its content was merged into Travel + Leisure and Golf Digest.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

