 including members of the Caribbean diaspora.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Site and Impact' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Tropic magazine is published quarterly in print and online, and has a growing following on social media platforms. Its website features additional content, including podcasts, video interviews, and online exclusives.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine has been praised for its contributions to diversifying and expanding the range of voices and perspectives represented in media coverage of the Caribbean region. Tropic has also been recognized for its efforts to bring attention to environmental and social justice issues in the region.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Conclusion' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Tropic is a quarterly print and online magazine, founded in 2019, focused on issues around culture, environment, and politics in the Caribbean region. It covers a range of topics related to social justice and the environment, with a focus on local and regional perspectives from the Caribbean. The magazine''s audience includes readers interested in Caribbean culture, environment, and politics, including members of the Caribbean diaspora. Tropic has been praised for its contributions to diversifying and expanding the range of voices and perspectives represented in media coverage of the Caribbean region.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

