VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription American periodical focused on parachuting, featuring skydiving techniques, gear reviews, safety advice, and event coverage.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Skydiving is an American-based publication focusing on the extreme sport of parachuting or skydiving. The magazine caters to those with a deep interest in the skydiving community, and it provides a broad range of content suited to both newcomers to the sport and experienced jumpers. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Content ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Skydiving Magazine covers everything from the basics of skydiving to the latest advancements in gear technology. It provides insight into techniques, safety procedures, and the science of skydiving, making it an essential resource for anyone interested in the sport. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Features in the magazine take an in-depth look at various elements of the sport, from personal narratives of unforgettable jumps to analytical pieces on how weather conditions and equipment manufacturing can affect jump performance. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition, the magazine profiles industry leaders, professional skydivers, and provides comprehensive reviews of skydiving gear, helping readers make informed decisions. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Moreover, the magazine covers global skydiving events, championships, and record-setting attempts, thus keeping the readers up-to-date with the happenings in the skydiving world. ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Publication History ' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Skydiving Magazine was first published in the 1970s and quickly gained a devoted readership due to its comprehensive coverage of the sport. The magazine enjoys a close relationship with the skydiving community and has been lauded for its dedication to promoting safety and education within the sport. Over the years, it has served as a reliable platform for skydivers and fans alike to stay connected and informed about the skydiving world.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

