ates, online discussion forums, and access to the full archive of past issues.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Overall, Operations magazine is an important and well-respected publication within the naval and maritime community, providing its readers with authoritative and insightful content on contemporary issues facing the seas.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

