(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Collaborations and Partnerships' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Impose has collaborated with a number of organizations and companies over the years. In 2015, the magazine partnered with the Northside Festival to host a series of concerts and events in Brooklyn.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine has also partnered with a number of brands to create branded content and sponsored features.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, Impose has established itself as one of the leading independent music and culture magazines in the United States. The magazine''s focus on emerging artists and commitment to independent editorial content has helped to establish its reputation as a respected voice in the industry.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

