(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, Improvement Era received a number of industry awards, including recognition from the Catholic Press Association.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Although Improvement Era ceased publication in 1970, its legacy lives on through The Ensign, which is still in circulation today. The magazine played an important role in the history of the LDS Church and helped to shape the beliefs and practices of its members around the world.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

