 seen as an important resource for parents and families to help create stronger bonds within their families.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Over the years, In the Family received a number of industry awards for its content and layout.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Although In the Family ceased publication in 1998, its influence on the LDS Church members and families continues to this day. Its focus on family life and spiritual development influenced generations of parents and families and continues in the Church''s emphasis on family activities and programs to strengthen the family unit within the Church.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

