ience and Reception' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'International Chess Magazine had a dedicated readership among serious chess enthusiasts and professionals around the world. The magazine was known for its high-quality content and thorough coverage of international chess events.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## Legacy' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Although International Chess Magazine is no longer in publication, it is recognized as an important and influential magazine in the history of chess. The magazine played a significant role in introducing new masters to the international chess community and promoting the latest developments in chess theory.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

