VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A magazine providing in-depth news, analysis, and photography of the National Association for Stock Car Auto Racing (NASCAR) Cup Series and other racing series for NASCAR enthusiasts, but ceased publication due to financial challenges.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'NASCAR Illustrated was a magazine that focused on news and analysis of the National Association for Stock Car Auto Racing (NASCAR) Cup Series and other racing series. The publication was founded in 2005, and had a total of 130 issues before it ceased publication in 2013.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine was aimed at NASCAR fans and provided in-depth coverage of the sport, including interviews with drivers and team members, race results and analysis, and stories on the history and culture of NASCAR. It also featured photography that captured the excitement and drama of NASCAR racing.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'NASCAR Illustrated was known for its high-quality journalism and innovative design. It won numerous awards, including the 2011 Folio Eddie Award for Best Sports Magazine. The magazine''s contributors included some of the most respected writers and photographers in the NASCAR world.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Despite its success, NASCAR Illustrated faced financial challenges due to the decline of print media and the changing landscape of sports journalism. It ceased publication in February 2013, leaving a gap in the market for NASCAR fans seeking professional, in-depth coverage of the sport.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

