VALUES ( N'Nuestro', N'nuestro', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A pioneering magazine promoting Latin American culture and civil rights advocacy in the United States from 1940 to 1961.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nuestro was a pioneering magazine aimed at the Latin American community in the United States. The magazine was published in English and Spanish from 1940 to 1961 and was based in Los Angeles.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nuestro was established by Sonny King, an African-American jazz singer, and activist who recognized the lack of representation of Latin Americans in mainstream media at the time. The magazine aimed to create a platform for Latin American voices, celebrating the culture and achievements of the Latin American community in the United States.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nuestro''s content was diverse and covered a broad range of topics that were relevant to the Latin American community, including politics, art, literature, and entertainment. Over the years, the magazine featured contributions from a wide range of writers, artists, and politicians, including Frida Kahlo, Langston Hughes, and Cesar Chavez.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nuestro was known for its advocacy of civil rights and social justice issues. The magazine played an important role in shaping the public discourse and challenging stereotypes associated with Latin American culture. Nuestro also showcased emerging talent in literature and art and provided a platform for Latin American writers and artists who were often overlooked by mainstream publishers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Despite its relatively short run, Nuestro became an influential publication that paved the way for other Latin American publications in the United States. The magazine''s legacy was felt in Latin American communities across the United States, and its contributions to promoting social justice and fighting prejudice and discrimination continue to inspire generations.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

-- NutriMag
INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'NutriMag', N'nutrimag', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A monthly health and wellness magazine providing practical tips and evidence-based advice for maintaining a healthy body and mind.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'NutriMag is a health and wellness magazine that provides information about nutrition, healthy living, and fitness. The magazine is published monthly in the United States and has a significant readership in the health and wellness industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'NutriMag was established in 2005 by a group of health and wellness enthusiasts who recognized the need for a trusted source of information about healthy living. The magazine''s content is designed to educate readers about the benefits of a healthy lifestyle and to provide practical tips and advice for maintaining a healthy body and mind.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine covers a diverse range of topics related to health and wellness, including nutrition, exercise, mental health, alternative medicine, and healthy lifestyle choices. NutriMag regularly features interviews with experts in the health and wellness field, as well as success stories from individuals who have achieved their health and fitness goals.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'NutriMag''s articles are well-researched and evidence-based, so readers can trust that the information provided is accurate and reliable. The magazine also provides readers with links to additional resources and references for further reading.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print publication, NutriMag has an online presence and also publishes an e-newsletter. The magazine''s website features additional articles, blogs, and videos related to health and wellness, allowing readers to access the latest information and stay up-to-date with the latest trends in the health and wellness industry.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

-- The Nuts & Bolts of PBM
INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'The Nuts & Bolts of PBM', N'the-nuts-and-bolts-of-pbm', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A bi-monthly trade magazine providing analysis and insights on the pharmacy benefit management (PBM) industry for professionals and stakeholders.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The Nuts & Bolts of PBM is a trade magazine in the United States that focuses on the pharmacy benefit management (PBM) industry. PBMs are intermediaries between health insurers and pharmacies, primarily responsible for negotiating drug prices, processing and handling pharmacy claims, and managing drug formularies.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The Nuts & Bolts of PBM was established in 1996 and is published bi-monthly. The magazine is primarily aimed at PBM executives and professionals, as well as healthcare executives, policymakers, and other stakeholders in the healthcare industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine''s content is focused on the PBM industry and provides readers with in-depth information on the latest trends, policy developments, and business strategies in the industry. The Nuts & Bolts of PBM also provides detailed analysis of PBM market data, industry research, and legislative and regulatory affairs.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The publication prides itself on providing insightful and reliable information to help PBMs and other stakeholders make informed decisions and navigate the complex and evolving PBM industry. The Nuts & Bolts of PBM is known for its well-researched articles, data analysis, and expert commentary, and is considered a leading voice in the PBM industry.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print publication, The Nuts & Bolts of PBM has an online presence, providing access to additional resources and the latest news and updates in the PBM industry. The magazine''s website also features a job board and advertising opportunities for businesses in the PBM industry.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

-- Nylon Guys
INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Nylon Guys', N'nylon-guys', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription A now defunct men''s fashion and lifestyle magazine that provided unique insights on fashion, music, and entertainment for a young urban male audience.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nylon Guys was a men''s fashion and lifestyle magazine that was published in the United States from 2004 to 2015. The magazine''s contents were focused on men''s fashion, grooming, lifestyle, music, and entertainment.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nylon Guys was a spin-off of the popular women''s fashion magazine, Nylon, which was founded in 1999. The magazine was originally titled "Nylon for Men" but was later rebranded as "Nylon Guys" in 2007 to reflect its independent identity.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'The magazine''s content was targeted towards a young, urban male audience interested in fashion and culture. Nylon Guys featured prominent actors, musicians, and athletes on its covers, including James Franco, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Ryan Reynolds, and Chris Pratt.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to fashion and lifestyle content, Nylon Guys also featured articles on art, design, technology, and current events, making it a well-rounded publication for readers interested in a variety of topics.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Nylon Guys was known for its unique design, playful tone, and editorial style, which stood out from more traditional men''s fashion publications. The magazine was also recognized for its coverage of emerging trends and designers, giving readers a sneak peek into the latest and greatest in men''s fashion.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In 2015, Nylon Guys ceased publication, as its parent company decided to focus exclusively on its women''s fashion and lifestyle magazine, Nylon. However, the magazine''s legacy lives on, as it inspired and influenced a generation of readers and designers.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

-- Fire Chief 
INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
VALUES ( N'Fire Chief ', N'fire-chief', 1, 'en' );
INSERT ArticleRevisions (ArticleId, [Text], RevisionReason, CreatedByAspNetUserId)
VALUES (SCOPE_IDENTITY(), N'{{ShortDescription Specialized resource for fire service leaders, detailing tactics, administration, innovation, and public safety issues.}}' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'"Fire Chief" is an American magazine created exclusively for leaders within the fire and rescue service industries. First established in 1956, the publication has functioned as a premier resource for higher-level firefighters all across the United States.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'With focal domains including emergent rescue techniques, administrative practices, fire service innovations and key aspects of public safety, "Fire Chief" explores a span of crucial topics that are pertinent within the field of fire rescue services. The primary readership includes fire chiefs, deputy fire chiefs, battalion chiefs, along with other influential individuals placed at strategic positions within various fire service departments.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Each issue of "Fire Chief" serves to highlight successful techniques and strategies, present data trends, provide expert insights, and even cover issues related to fire litigation and policy making. By doing so, the magazine assists fire service administrators and managers in making strategic decisions that have profound impacts on manpower, resources, budgeting, safety practices, and overall departmental efficiency.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'Renowned contributors from various spheres of fire service, including fire chiefs and captains, fire safety experts, firefighters, paramedics, and fire-safety researchers, all find a place in the insightful pages of "Fire Chief". This leads to a multi-faceted exploration of perspectives, encapsulating real-world advice alongside cutting-edge research and discovery in fire service.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its physical distribution, the magazine also maintains a strong digital presence, offering its wide readership the option for accessing archived issues and engaging with a community of experienced professionals through online forums. As a result, "Fire Chief" fosters an environment of learning, growth, and collaboration amongst fire service individuals both within and beyond American borders.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

-- The American Boy
INSERT Articles (Title, UrlSlug, SiteId, Culture)
