st technology and trends in the industry. The magazine has won numerous awards over the years, including the coveted Jesse H. Neal National Business Journalism Award.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'In addition to its print publication, High Performance has maintained a strong online presence, providing exclusive content and multimedia features to its readers.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'## References' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "High Performance Magazine." Hot Rod Network. Accessed August 31, 2021.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "High Performance Magazine." Hemmings. Accessed August 31, 2021.' + CHAR(13) + CHAR(10) + N'- "Joe R. Hrudka." National Hot Rod Association. Accessed August 31, 2021.{{Categories Magazines}}', N'Article created.', '7240be61-df81-46f9-8152-6a48b96abc40');

